-- Private equity firm Everstone hires top Goldman official as CEO
-- By Indulal PM
-- Tue Aug 19, 2014 01:05AM EDT
-- None



MUMBAI, Aug 19 (Reuters) - India-focused private equity fund Everstone Group has hired a top executive from Goldman Sachs <GS.N> in Asia as its new chief executive, it said on Tuesday.

L. Brooks Entwistle was most recently chairman of Goldman Sachs Southeast Asia and CEO of the investment bank's Singapore operations. He will continue to be based in Singapore and oversee Everstone's day-to-day management as well as lead transactions and originate deals, according to the Everstone statement. Entwistle also spent time in Mumbai as CEO and founder of Goldman Sachs India, according to Everstone.